Revision history for JavaScript class HTTP.Query.

0.03  2005-07-13T02:53:51
      - The constructor now uses window.document.location.search as the
        default query string if none is provided. Suggested by Marshall Roch.
      - The toString() method now takes an optional argument to specify "&" as
        an alternate argument delimiter.

0.02  2005-07-12T18:22:26
      - Minor documentation tweaks.
      - Added more tests.
      - Fixed act() to properly iterate over all GET arguments.
      - Added toString() method.

0.01  2005-07-12T06:35:39
      - Initial public release.
